Canvas: Darkmode is simple extension that applies a dark theme to Instructure's Canvas that saves power, prevents eye strain and provides a more modern feel. 

It works on any "*.instructure.com" URL as well as most "canvas.*.edu" URLs. 

It collects does not collect any data and is open-source. Feel free to check it out and modify it if you have any issues!
